{"tid":983353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【脫歐亂局】憂慮硬脫歐 一家五口儲定日用品夠用4個月","createTime":"2019-01-16T01:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T02:07:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e53204e6ca798a6803aa8f99216e96c5d8b0c66d","tid":983353,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T01:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190115/large/1547533770_6fd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190115%2Flarge%2F1547533770_6fd7.jpg&h=6f1d78b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國一個家庭自英國脫歐談判開始，就逐漸在家儲起一大堆食物及日用品，為無協議脫歐後的情況作準備。他們稱這些物資足夠他們生活4個月。 <br />\n<br />\n住在康沃爾（Cornwall）的曼氏夫婦（Richard and Nevine Mann）育有3名小孩，雖然英國3月才脫歐，36歲的曼太太早與37歲先生儲備物資。她說：「不久前我們意識到可能會出現無協議脫歐，若果真的發生，短期內物資供應會出現問題，所以我們開始購買平常會用的物品。我們買了很多豆及米，夠我們吃4個月。」<br />\n<br />\n她們買了大量食物，現在櫃子已有52罐豆、16罐吞拿魚、一大桶蛋黃醬、8罐碎番茄及4罐番茄汁。另外也有2大桶奶粉、數包米、意粉等。 <br />\n<br />\n曼太太說：「有一些食物我們不會常常買，如蔬菜及奶粉。我們有焗豆、鷹嘴豆、意粉。飲品方面有茶、咖啡等&hellip;&hellip;我們差不多足夠了，所以會慢慢減少購買。我們沒有買得過火，假設未能達成協議，這樣做可令我們順利度過數個月。」<br />\n<br />\n除了大量食物，一家人也買了種子及潔淨雨水儀器，可隨時在花園自耕自給。另外曼太太要服用抗癲癇及薄血藥物，所以也儲備了藥物等。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190116/58967860\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F58967860&d=e6KkJSHDiHBqtimTWL5KHywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ca9e7ed0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F58967860&h=cb75b388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190116/58967860</a>"},{"pid":"f1d3865c1e549512f0e7ecd5df505c1341680bac","tid":983353,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T01:42:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港獨聯 關愛座hunter<br />\n都買左好多祖國貨物做儲備<br />\nskr skr<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"5d11fecb19f374a9795e63f34fff75d084df07d0","tid":983353,"uid":26602,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T01:59:20.000Z","msg":"我諗起以前高登有位巴打為應付世界末日儲左成堆糧食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c518a26cb9106ba0f0387fdc267c0600420e9106","tid":983353,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d11fecb19f374a9795e63f34fff75d084df07d0","tid":983353,"uid":26602,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T01:59:20.000Z","msg":"我諗起以前高登有位巴打為應付世界末日儲左成堆糧食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:03:03.000Z","msg":"午餐肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4a19d4056116d10ee231e97e58c1644f769c48","tid":983353,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c518a26cb9106ba0f0387fdc267c0600420e9106","tid":983353,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d11fecb19f374a9795e63f34fff75d084df07d0","tid":983353,"uid":26602,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T01:59:20.000Z","msg":"我諗起以前高登有位巴打為應付世界末日儲左成堆糧食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:03:03.000Z","msg":"午餐肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:07:25.000Z","msg":"一桶桶水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}